    "comments": [
      "\"This is Boxing Day, just in case you've only just woken up, and I'm Tommy Vance, and it's a pleasure to be with you. Tonight we're going to feature some very good session material and some live concert material we thought you might like to hear.\" (This intro is on a) only.)",
